reviewText: I got this DVD not only because it's a one of a kind, but because the voice of this spectacular Superstar.  She will always live on thru her music.  If your fan this is a must have.
my disc is in perfect condtion but the music sounds slightly scratchy or like you put cellophane in your ears before you listened...very odd

I received this item within 2 days of ordering, I love Whitney Houston's music &  was surprised to see she had a x-mas dvd out, so i jumped at the chance to purchase this even thou Christmas is still 3 months away. I rate this seller a 5 (EXCELLENT),  & I will order from this company again.
It was a Christmas present for my mother.  She loves Whitney Houston. She loved it.
This is not a good DVD, I would not buy it again.  This is a sham
Whitney has such a gorgeous voice.  I'm think she is singing with the angels for the Lord!  I really love this album!
Whitney Elizabeth Houston singing while a yule tide fire burns.....is there a better way to spend the Christmas holiday ?
a must have for Christmas for any whitney fan.  if you are  feeling down, this will perk you right up with holiday joy!
I was surprised to find out that I read the discrption wrong. I thought that this was videos of her Christmas songs. Didn't know it was only the songs played to a picture of a yule log.
